<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #EF4444; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
      .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; }
      .fee-info { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #EF4444; margin: 20px 0; }
      .amount { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #EF4444; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>New Fee Assessment</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= @recipient.name %>!</h2>
        
        <p>This is to inform you about a new fee assessment for your child:</p>
        
        <div class="fee-info">
          <p><strong>Student:</strong> <%= @student.full_name %></p>
          <p><strong>Fee Category:</strong> <%= @fee.fee_category&.name || 'General' %></p>
          <p><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @fee.description %></p>
          <p><strong>Amount:</strong> <span class="amount">$<%= @fee.amount %></span></p>
          <p><strong>Due Date:</strong> <%= @fee.due_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
          <p><strong>Created:</strong> <%= @fee.created_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Please ensure payment is made by the due date to avoid any late fees.</p>
        
        <p>For payment options or questions, please contact the school administration.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for using Kid Garden!</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Kid Garden. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>